DarkMouse::

She left her room and went to the messhall.  She got herself some 
energon and sat down.  She was still upset over the fight. But a bot 
can't dwell on the past forever. For now, she wanted to get back to 
the console and start scanning. Those dragons had to have taken that 
bot somewhere and she wanted to know where. Her curiousity was 
starting to get the better of her.  She grabbed her mug and went to 
the bridge where she took her place at the security and 
communications console.  She started scanning all wave lengths and 
all frequencies trying to find those that took that blasted cat.
